    "39801": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Amber",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "You guys are back! The Honorary Knight returns triumphant!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Yup, {NICKNAME}'s back from tussling with Dvalin!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "You just returned yesterday, right? Jean got back first, and she told us all about your heroic deeds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "*sigh* I wonder if I'll ever get an opportunity like that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "All thanks to your referral."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "That doesn't come into it. You guys deserve all the credit for how you resolved this crisis."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "When I brought you into the city that day, I was just doing my duty as an Outrider."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Trust me, it's not an opportunity you'd want too often..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "You're right, actually. Peace is hard-won, and we shouldn't take it for granted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "And this time, you're the one we should all be grateful to."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You're welcome! ...But, have you been waiting for us here this whole time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Of course not! Just because I'm not out on the front line doesn't mean I don't have work to do... In fact, I'm dealing with the aftermath of the crisis as we speak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aftermath? Here? What happened in Mondstadt?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "While Master Jean was away, the monsters lurking nearby made a coordinated attack on the city."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Fortunately, we weren't completely taken by surprise. I detected the hilichurls were moving closer to the city a while back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh yeah! Paimon remembers. When we first met, you were clearing out one of their camps..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Exactly. And if we hadn't started making preparations back then, Mondstadt would be in much greater danger by now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Glad you held them off."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Me too. But I have a strange feeling that we're not out of the woods yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Hilichurls aren't usually capable of coordinating like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why would the hilichurls do this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I know, it's strange. Hilichurls aren't usually capable of coordinating like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Our best guess is that the Abyss Order is behind it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "They've taken over the hilichurls? Hmm... Good thing we saved Dvalin, or they might've taken him, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "That's right. And since I'm the Outrider, it's up to me to keep eyes on the Abyss Order from now on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Ugh, I'm sorry. You should be celebrating your victory, not listening to all this somber talk!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Hmm... I promised to take you out for some Sticky Honey Roast, didn't I? Before everyone got caught up in the Stormterror crisis."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "There's no time like the present, right? You guys hungry?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You bet! You may have forgotten till just now, but it's been on Paimon's mind this whole time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Awesome, let's go! It's been way too long since I last ate a Sticky Honey Roast myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Wait for me at <color=#00E1FFFF>Good Hunter</color>. I'll be right there, I just have to clean up here real quick."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "39802": {
        "Desc": "Chat with the locals (Cyrus)",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Grace",
                    "T": "So, Stormterror's true identity is Dvalin — one of the Four Winds! We never should've forgotten his past sacrifice for Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Grace",
                    "T": "Every cloud has a silver lining — we're fortunate that our relationship with the Dragon of the East didn't sour past the point of no return."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Grace",
                    "T": "For that, we have you to thank. And Jean, for her unfailing devotion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Grace",
                    "T": "As long as we have the Knights of Favonius, peace and freedom will prevail in Mondstadt."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "39803": {
        "Desc": "Chat with the locals (Nimrod)",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Nimrod",
                    "T": "Long live the heroes! Thank you, it's finally over."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nimrod",
                    "T": "Many trade routes have closed due to the Stormterror incident. We can cope for now without fresh fruit and vegetables... But if the wine supply dries up, we're all doomed!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nimrod",
                    "T": "I cannot imagine a world without wine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nimrod",
                    "T": "I hope they get the trade routes back up and running soon."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "39804": {
        "Desc": "Chat with the locals (Grace)",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "Here we go! This is it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "Crisis! Danger! The thrill of adventure!!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "Adventurers' Guild! Finally, our days of rescuing kittens and finding lost puppies are over! The age of adventure is upon us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "Roll up, youngsters, join the Adventurers' Guild today! In this time of great upheaval, we must rally together, take on the dragon, and save our great city of Mondstadt!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yeah, about that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "...What!? WHAT!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "The Stormterror threat is resolved? I missed the Acting Grand Master's speech?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyrus",
                    "T": "...Bah! Stormterror should have put up more of a fight! We didn't get to join in..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
