    "39807": {
        "Desc": "Go to Good Hunter",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sara",
                    "T": "Greetings, may I take your order?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Why so cold? I've always thought that we enjoy quite the intimate friendship."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Oh hey, I didn't see you there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Hahaha... It seems your great battle sharpened not only your combat skills but your wit as well. A knight after my own heart."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ah, the handsome Mr. Kaeya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Ah, so you do feel something for me. And people say my charm is fake."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "To bask in the presence of Mondstadt's new big hero is quite the morale boost. And that's coming from a knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sweet-talking sugar-coated Captain Kaeya..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Haha, nonsense! I speak from the heart."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Just looking for a quiet spot to collect my thoughts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "While all the other knights are working hard to clean up after the battle..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Thinking can be an arduous task, you know. Believe me, I'd much rather be taking out the trash."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you plotting this time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Me? Nothing. On the contrary, I'm trying to work out what others are plotting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "That's why I'm here — somewhere quiet, where I can collect my thoughts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, whatcha thinkin' about, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "The Abyss Order."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "A dragon wreaks havoc in Mondstadt, and the Acting Grand Master leaves the city to combat the threat. Strategically, that's the perfect moment for the Abyss Order to make their move."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "If you were the Abyss Order, would you squander this golden opportunity by sending in nothing more than a few hilichurls?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're right, it doesn't add up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There must be more to this story."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "To get to the bottom of it, I decided to wait. So I waited, and watched for their next move."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Then came the day you made all hell break loose in Stormterror's Lair, just as the hilichurls' cries sounded from the city gates..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "That same day, I saw shadowy figures lurking in the city itself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Inside the city!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Well, all the other knights were outside, fighting the enemy. As you can imagine, that left the inside of the city completely unguarded."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Except for me, of course. And so I approached the Abyss Order infiltrators for a bit of... hmm, let's call it fraternizing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Through various means, I managed to gather some rather interesting intel."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "The situation is this: The Abyss Order... they are united under a single leader."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Abyss Order has a leader?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Yes. And it was this very leader who devised the plot to turn Dvalin into a weapon of war."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What exactly did you have to do to find this out!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Hehehe... Let's just say I'm blessed with certain linguistic powers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "#There's more... The Abyss Order has a name for this leader... They call {F#him \"The Prince.\"}{M#her \"The Princess.\"}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#{F#Prince...}{M#Princess...}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Now, I'm sorry to cut this intelligence briefing short, but I do believe I spy Amber heading this way..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I think she's still angry with me for my absence from the defense effort during the attack... I'd better slip away before she notices me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "One minute I see Kaeya, the next he's slipped away! Clear sign of a guilty conscience..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He does a lot behind the scenes..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Are you sure? Because that sounds like exactly what he'd say to talk himself out of trouble..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I know! What a scoundrel!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I agree. He sets a terrible example for someone who's Cavalry Captain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "But let's forget about him. I worked super hard today and my tummy's rumbling. Let's order!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Hi Sara! One Sticky Honey Roast, please..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
