    "39607": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "If you want to chat, now's the time — a bard stays not always in a single clime."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About Dvalin..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Up till the end, Dvalin remembered his duty as one of the Four Winds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "As such, I don't intend to forcibly strip him of that duty and force my ideals of freedom onto him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I just hope that Dvalin will be able to choose for himself and understand what freedom is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Before I became an archon, I too was taught the meaning of freedom in this way by a friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the Abyss Order..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Kaeya shared some new intelligence, you say?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#...I see. So, the Abyss Order has a {F#Prince}{M#Princess} who orchestrated the plan to corrupt Dvalin?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#They were probably trying to turn Dvalin into a weapon of war for the Abyss. But that said, I have never heard of any such {F#Prince}{M#Princess} of the Abyss Order."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not an Abyss Order tradition, then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So this is a recent development..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I think so, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#Apparently, but how does a {F#Prince}{M#Princess} come out of nowhere and take command over the entire Abyss Order?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About Signora..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That Fatui lady didn't hang around, did she? She just grabbed your Gnosis and left!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "She wanted to avoid any eyewitnesses from the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "The slightest slip-up here would have destroyed the Fatui's diplomatic relations with the Knights."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So they're just gonna keep acting like Mondstadt's allies as if nothing happened!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "*sigh*... If only the seven nations had banded together against the Abyss Order in the first place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "The Fatui possess the strongest military among the seven nations. Yet they've used it to steal the Holy Lyre, covet the power of gods, and use Dvalin as a bargaining chip against the Knights..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of the Lyre... didn't Diluc say something like this before?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He said that the Fatui can only run amok across the seven nations and threaten the Knights because of the harbingers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Yes. As I said earlier, the Cryo Archon has given them authority and strength beyond that of other mortals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "The Tsaritsa... I haven't seen her in five hundred years. What is she thinking? What's her plan?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Whatever the answer is, I have a feeling it's only going to make your search for The Seven all the more difficult..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About deities..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "As I said before, Vision wielders are known as allogenes and may ascend to Celestia."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "A Gnosis is a higher-order nexus of elemental manipulation and is emblematic of an archon's status as one of The Seven."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#But as for which of The Seven took your {F#brother}{M#sister}... I'm sorry, I don't know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "...Wait, as one of the Seven, I'm not clear of suspicion yet either, am I?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You don't look like that god at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hang on a hot second! Tone-Deaf Bard is just one of Barbatos' many incarnations, who's to say—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We've known you long enough to trust you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#Haha, we're a great team indeed! Say, once you find your {F#brother}{M#sister}, how would you like to become one of the new Four Winds?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Perhaps..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hmm, you don't seem too into it, {NICKNAME}..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Tone-Deaf Bard... If being one of the Four Winds means free food, you can consider Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Hahaha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's nothing else..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Well then, best be off to <color=#00E1FFFF>Liyue</color>. If the descension ritual you fail to tally, then another year you must dally."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
